item-argocyte-armor-heavy = An extremely heavy piece of armor that protects against excessive damage.
item-argocyte-armor-light = An almost weightless piece of armor that protects against excessive damage. Extremely vulnerable to explosions.
item-argocyte-helmet-heavy = A heavy helmet made of argocyte plating.
item-argocyte-helmet-light = A light helmet made of argocyte plating. Feels light as a feather, but will easily shatter during explosions.
item-argocyte-gauntlets-heavy = Simple insulated gloves with large argocyte plates sewn on. Lends your fists some serious potential for harm.
item-argocyte-gauntlets-light = Simple insulated gloves with small argocyte plates sewn on. Lends your fists some potential for harm.
item-argocyte-boots-heavy = Hard-looking boots made out of argocyte armor plates . They're very heavy.
item-argocyte-boots-light = Brittle-looking boots made out of argocyte armor plates . They're very light, but may break when exploded.